title: U.S. Coronavirus Quarantine Coming Soon!
itunes:author: Andrew Schulz's Flagrant with Akaash Singh
itunes:summary: What up people. I just got off the phone with some folks that are currently in Italy. They broke down to me whats happening and what WILL happen in the U.S. very soon. Prepare yourselves and spread the word so your friends and family will be ready.
